************************************************
Welcome to sowatflinc_ptx, version 0.2 (06/2009)
************************************************

Usage : enter T in Celsius, P in bar and X in mole fraction NaCl
Properties returned are the phase state, the molar volume, the
composition and heat capacities of the phases.

Notice that the heat capacities are computed from a formula
that is corrected by a factor of 1/(1+x) that was missed in the
original publication. Error reports send to thomas.driesner@erdw.ethz.ch.
